Task: SW1

VLAN 10, 20, 99
10 = SALES
20 = IT
99 = NATIVE
Untagged VLAN 99
Etherchannel LACP, Active
e0/0 + e0/1 = p1
Port-Channel must be Trunking
VLAN 10 = e0/2
VLAN 20 = e0/3
int e0/2 and e0/3 should be access ports

Configuration: SW1

en
conf t
hostname SW1
vlan 10
name SALES
vlan 20
name IT
vlan 99
name NATIVE
int range e0/0-1
channel-protocol lacp
channel-group 1 mode active
int p1
switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk native vlan 99
switchport trunk allowed vlan 10,20,99
int e0/2
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 10
int e0/3
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 20
exit
do wr
